name: Bed Queen size Mattress Boxspring Frame Headboard (HOPATCONG)
description:
I have a queen size mattress in fair to good shape. Our home and mattress and everything is bed bug free and smoke free and we have never had either in our home. It will come qith a cover.
You can also have the box spring for free. In good to great shape.
Please text or call when you are ready to come. I will hold if you are on your way.
We have 3 metal frame sets to choose from for free, or take all of them.
We have 2 different wooden headboards for you to make an offer on. One comes with a repairable but free matching footboard.
